title: Send Me Nutrolls, Fire Me Over It
description: What's that house worth?, we write our own Personal Ads, Rockstar or Not, Group Therapy, Dave thinks people in the front rows at concerts need to be having fun and clapping or else they shouldn't sit there, Cold Reading Jokes, War of the Roses, and more!
